Methods.S:
Two series of sections were incubated in rabbit antiPHA-L 
    antiserum (1:2000; Dakopatts, Denmark) for 18 hours at 4"C, 
    followed by incubations in swine anti-rabbit whole serum (1:50; 
    Nordic Immunology, The Netherlands) and in rabbit-PAP (1:800; 
    Dakopatts, Denmark), respectively, each for 1 hour at 20°C.

Discussion.S:
Beckstead, '79; Newman and Winans, '80a,b; 
    Reep and Winans, '82; Christie et al., '87; Fuller et 
    al., '87; McGeorge and Faull, '89).
